extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Realtime rest API to monitor newly created JIRA issues. This is configured as webhook in JIRA. Every time new JIRA issue is created under a specific project, API invokes utility methods to take necessary actions (automating the extraction of attached log files for example).

  div(id="container")
    h1 List of newly created JIRA issues (Project: ECSS and Status:Open) and its attachments:
    table(id="issuelist", border="1")
      tr
        th JIRA ID
        th JIRA Summary
        th JIRA Attachments
      